Rachel Leskovac https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rachel_Leskovac 0 Rachel Leskovac (born 5 June 1976) is an Olivier award-nominated English actress and singer best known for her television roles as teacher Lara Heaton in Shameless, hairdresser Natasha Blakeman in Coronation Street, and Joanne Cardsley in Hollyoaks.
